inistrador por otro medio.\nOcurrió un error de validación. Por favor, confirme los campos y envíe el formulario de nuevo.\nFalló el envío del mensaje. Por favor, inténtelo más tarde o contacte con el administrador por otro medio.\nPor favor, acepte los términos y condiciones para continuar.\nPlease fill in the required field.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.','Formulario de contacto 1','','publish','open','open','','formulario-de-contacto-1','','','2015-02-24 09:23:56','2015-02-24 09:23:56','',0,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=26',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(28,1,'2015-02-24 09:31:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Welcome to my <a href=\"http://www.prelovac.com/vladimir/wordpress-plugins/wp-wall\">WP Wall</a> Guestbook!','WP Wall Guestbook','','draft','open','open','','','','','2015-02-24 09:31:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?page_id=28',0,'page','',0),(29,1,'2015-02-24 09:33:37','2015-02-24 09:33:37',' ','','','publish','open','open','','29','','','2015-02-24 09:35:45','2015-02-24 09:35:45','',0,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?p=29',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(30,1,'2015-02-24 09:33:37','2015-02-24 09:33:37',' ','','','publish','open','open','','30','','','2015-02-24 09:35:45','2015-02-24 09:35:45','',6,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?p=30',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(31,1,'2015-02-24 09:33:37','2015-02-24 09:33:37',' ','','','publish','open','open','','31','','','2015-02-24 09:35:45','2015-02-24 09:35:45','',6,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?p=31',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(32,1,'2015-02-24 09:33:37','2015-02-24 09:33:37',' ','','','publish','open','open','','32','','','2015-02-24 09:35:45','2015-02-24 09:35:45','',6,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?p=32',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(33,1,'2015-02-24 09:33:37','2015-02-24 09:33:37',' ','','','publish','open','open','','33','','','2015-02-24 09:35:45','2015-02-24 09:35:45','',0,'http://localhost/Proyecto/wordpress/?p=